### Login to Unidigital API
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "UserName": "{{user}}",
    "Password": "{{password}}"
}


### Consultar primer documento
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/first
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Serie": "{{seriesStrongId}}",
    "Type": "FA"
}

### Consultar ultimo documento
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/last
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Serie": "{{seriesStrongId}}",
    "Type": "FA"
}

### Consultar Documento por StrongId recibe JSON
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/viewjson/43a92ac7-d186-41e7-98ef-6931c0ee00a9
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}



### Consultar Documento por Número de control
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/controlnumber/8035
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Consultar Documento por Numero de Serie
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/searchbynumberandserie
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Number":"347556",
    "Serie": "3b633c48-271a-459f-bc8e-a35139d3a0ae",
    "DocumentType":"FA"
}

### Consultar Númnero de Control de Ciclo por Fecha
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/controlnumbers?fromDate=2024-1-1%2000%3A00%3A00&toDate=2024-1-30%2023%3A59%3A59
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear Ciclo de Facturación
POST {{baseUrl}}/batch/open 
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "SerieStrongId": "{{seriesStrongId}}"
}


### Consultar Ciclo de Facturación por StrongId
GET {{baseUrl}}/batch/ddfb898d-f400-4ef7-9abe-b021f807902e
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

