### Listar Lotes
GET {{baseUrl}}/batch/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "Status": 2,
   "Date": "2025-06-11"
}

### Listar Documentos por Fecha
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/list?page=1&thefrom=2024-07-01 00:00:00&theTo=2024-07-30 23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Aprobar Lote de Facturación
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches/:id/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Cerrar Ciclo de Facturación
POST {{baseUrl}}/batch/close
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Id": "44bf7602-1ecb-4129-91c5-70a3fb6f51d3"
}

### Cancelar Ciclo de Facturación
POST {{baseUrl}}/batch/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Id": "ddfb898d-f400-4ef7-9abe-b021f807902e"
}
